Description:

    To create a centralized bill management system for sharehouses. The web application will be built with PHP/CSS/HTML

Functional Requirements:    
  
    Sharehouse related functions: 
     Creating a sharehouse
      Defining a sharehouse leader
     Adding/removing sharehouse members
     Household overview including history of sharehouse and its outstanding bills 
     Store bank account details
     Mark and confirm payment from sharehouse leader and members

    Bill related functions:
     Inserting bill
     Bill upload/download
     Viewing a bill
     Paying a bill (once-off and periodic bills with fixed and variable charges)
     Bill notification via email
     Requesting bill payment via email from sharehouse members
     Verify bills as valid
     Ability to mark bills as paid
     Bill reminders by email and on overview
     Notes and comments on each bill

